## What This Module Does

This module ports the "Depth Fracture Datamosh" effect from VJlive-2. It detects spatial discontinuities (edges) in the depth map to create a "fracture map". Datamosh artifacts, prismatic color bleeding, and pixel displacement are then concentrated strictly along these physical fracture lines, creating a shattered glass aesthetic synchronized to the real-world geometry.

---

## What It Does NOT Do

- It does NOT render 3D physics-based shattering. It is a 2D screen-space pixel shader tracking depth edges.

